76
00:04:17,150 --> 00:04:19,150
[ Chuckles ] HI, BABY.

77
00:04:19,150 --> 00:04:23,160
AND THIS IS MY BOY,  AND THIS IS, UH,

78
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:26,160
UH, UH, WAIT.

