00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:29,160
MY AGENT.  MY AGENT.

80
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:34,670
I GOTTA PLAY THIS WEEKEND. IF I PLAY 65% OF MY GAMES, I GET A BONUS.

81
00:04:34,670 --> 00:04:38,670
I GOTTA GET THE BONUS.

82
00:04:38,670 --> 00:04:40,670
OKAY, JESSE. YOU TAKE CARE, LITTLE GUY.

83
00:04:41,170 --> 00:04:42,680
MR. MAGUIRE? YEAH?

84
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:46,180
THIS IS HIS FOURTH CONCUSSION. SHOULDN'TSOMEBODY GET HIM TO STOP?

85
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:51,180
- [ Beeper Beeping ]  - IT WOULD TAKE A TANK    TO STOP YOUR DAD.

86
00:04:51,180 --> 00:04:56,190
IT WOULD TAKE ALL FIVE SUPER TROOPER VR WARRIORS...

87
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:59,190
TO STOP YOUR DAD.

88
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:01,190
RIGHT?

89
00:05:01,190 --> 00:05:04,200
RIGHT?

90
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:06,200
FUCK YOU.

91
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:12,700
