150
00:09:00,430 --> 00:09:02,940
WOULD YOU LIKE ME-- OH, NO, NO. THAT'S FINE.

151
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,440
THANK YOU.

152
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:11,940
[ Phones Ringing ] I COULD CONNECT YOU, IF YOU'D LIKE.

153
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:14,450
