156
00:09:32,470 --> 00:09:35,970
ALL RIGHT! HEY, FINALLY SOMEBODY SANE.

157
00:09:37,970 --> 00:09:41,470
[ Man ] GOOD WORK, MAGUIRE! [ Man ]  YEAH, YEAH!

158
00:09:41,470 --> 00:09:44,980
YEAH! [ Cheering ]

159
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:48,980
[ Man ] UNBELIEVABLE. UNBELIEVABLE.

160
00:09:48,980 --> 00:09:51,980
[ Cheering Continues ]

161
00:09:51,980 --> 00:09:53,990
OH, YEAH.

