176
00:10:37,530 --> 00:10:40,030
- [ Coughing Continues ] - [ Both ]  OHH!

177
00:10:40,030 --> 00:10:43,030
I'M SORRY IF I WAS RUDE JUST THEN.

178
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:46,040
THAT'S OKAY.  WE'RE IN IT TOGETHER NOW.

179
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:50,040
