00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:56,050
TELL ME HOW YOU PROPOSED. HONEY, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT? YOU WANT SOME JUICE?

182
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:58,050
[ Baby Continues Crying ]

183
00:10:58,550 --> 00:11:03,560
THANK YOU. BUT WE'RE HIKING UP THROUGH THE POOLS.

184
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:08,560
I GOT THE RING IN MY POCKET, AND--  [ Laughs ] I'M A LITTLE NERVOUS.

185
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:12,060
I'M LAGGING, YOU KNOW, AND SHE SAYS TO ME-- GET THIS--

186
00:11:12,570 --> 00:11:14,070
"HURRY UP, KLUTZ."

187
00:11:14,570 --> 00:11:17,070
IT BOTHERED ME SOMEWHAT, YOU KNOW?

188
00:11:17,070 --> 00:11:19,070
