195
00:11:37,590 --> 00:11:40,090
THAT MY ASSISTANT HAS ASSUMED  THAT I'VE NOW PROPOSED.

196
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:43,600
SO SHE'S GOTTEN A LOUNGE BAND TO ACTUALLY PLAY "HERE COMES THE BRIDE"...

197
00:11:44,100 --> 00:11:46,600
