200
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:55,110
SO I TURNED TO HER, SORT OF GRANDLY SAY,

201
00:11:55,610 --> 00:11:58,610
"WELL, THIS IS ME, KLUTZ,

202
00:11:58,610 --> 00:12:02,110
ASKING YOU, GODDESS OF ROCK CLIMBING, TO MARRY ME."

203
00:12:02,620 --> 00:12:04,120
